{c_label}Cooldown: {/c}{c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Raheir brutalizes the ground, dealing {if:SF_10}{c_number}{payload:GROUNDSLAM_PAYLOAD}{/c}{else}massive{/if} Physical damage and Slowing enemies by {c_number}[{SF_4}*100|%|]{/c} for {c_number}{SF_0}{/c} seconds. Targets in the center of the slam are Slowed by {c_number}[{SF_5}*100|%|]{/c} instead.

Selecting a Mercenary Core Skill alters their wielded Weapon and Basic Attack.
{c_label}Weapon:{/c} {c_important}Round Shield{/c}
{c_label}Basic Attack:{/c} {c_important}Shield Strike{/c}
Raheir swings a round shield at enemies, dealing {if:SF_10}{c_number}{payload:MELEE_PAYLOAD_TOOLTIP}{/c}{else}moderate{/if} Physical damage. Every {c_number}{SF_8}{/c} swings, Raheir Heals you for {c_number}[{SF_7}*100]%{/c} of your Maximum Life.
